Privacy and Security Policy

At Virus Onslaught, we prioritize the privacy and security of our users. Our commitment to safeguarding your personal information is paramount, and we adhere to strict policies to ensure your data remains protected. Below is an outline of our Privacy and Security Policy:

No Advertising: Virus Onslaught does not feature any third-party advertisements within the app. We believe in providing a seamless and uninterrupted gaming experience without the intrusion of ads.

Data Collection: We do not collect any personally identifiable information from our users. This includes but is not limited to names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any other sensitive data.

Data Encryption: Any data transmitted between the app and our servers is encrypted to ensure its security and integrity. We utilize industry-standard encryption protocols to protect your information from unauthorized access.

Data Retention: We don't retain any user data.

Policy Updates: This Privacy and Security Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in legal or regulatory requirements, technological advancements, or updates to our practices. Users will be notified of any significant changes to the policy.

By using Virus Onslaught, you acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy and Security Policy. If you have any questions or concerns about our policies or practices, please contact us at aregoniks@gmail.com.
